name: Chrome Dino 🦖🦖 ~ Shit.!! I Still Suck.!!
description:
This is the 2nd Piece in a series of 3.

This simple infinite runner sees you jump over cacti and dodge underneath obstacles.

This often-overlooked Easter Egg in Google Chrome appears when you try to visit a website while disconnected from the Internet.

The Chrome Dino game is a play on going back to the 'prehistoric age' when you had no Wi-Fi.
